subject: Hello, greetings to you.
body:
Hello, greetings to you.
Please did you receive my previous messages i sent to you? I am waiting to hear from you.
 Thank you.
Mr. Andrew

subject: Re: Hello, greetings to you.
body:
Hello Mr. Andrew,

I hope you're doing well. I'm not sure if I received your previous messages, could you please tell me what they were about? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Janice
